config AUDIO_CODEC_DUMMY_STUB
	bool "Dummy audio codec driver stub"
	depends on DT_HAS_ZEPHYR_CODEC_DUMMY_STUB_ENABLED
	help
	  Enable the dummy audio codec driver that can be used for testing and development purposes without requiring actual hardware.
	  The driver implements the necessary interfaces but does not perform any real audio processing.
